        "BeginAnim": "DialogEnable",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Directions, objectives, combat techniques, assigned tasks—these were the indelible protocols embedded in Veronica\\'s consciousness from her life as a mechanical gladiator.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 5,
        "ActionId": 5,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'And yet she\\'s never been programmed to know what to do when she\\'s presented with an infinite number of paths to choose from down the road.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 6,
        "ActionId": 6,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The human mind, adaptable as it is, would know what to do in this situation better than the calculating mind of a mechanoid, except there is not a single human left to guide her now.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 7,
        "ActionId": 7,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The girl who was once her teacher on all things human is no longer able to answer any of her questions.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 8,
        "ActionId": 8,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Human bodies contain no data storage modules to preserve memories and thoughts, making death irreversible once life vanishes from their ever-so fragile carnal shell.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 9,
        "ActionId": 9,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Why is it, then, that she can\\'t bring herself to let go of the lifeless human body in her arms?'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 10,
        "ActionId": 10,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Veronica has no answer to this question. She simply continues her solitary journey across the endless snowfield.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 11,
        "ActionId": 11,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Snowflakes settle gently upon Serra\\'s body, and yet these delicate crystals will never melt.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 12,
        "ActionId": 12,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Veronica presses on against the biting wind, leaving a trail of footprints across the barren wilderness.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 13,
        "ActionId": 13,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": "DialogDisable",
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'A mechanoid\\'s consciousness only registers the data markers of each day\\'s beginning and end, unable to grasp the true meaning of \"time.\"'}"
    },
    {
