        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Yet in her consciousness module, Veronica feels a flutter. Something within her mechanisms falters for just a moment, as if trying to convey an emotion beyond a mechanoid\\'s interpretation.'}"
    },
    {
