        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The concept of graves and what they meant was only mentioned in passing when Veronica and Serra compared human body decay to the deterioration of machinery.'}"
